MALACAÑANG Manila

PROCLAMATION NO. 1220

CREATING AND DESIGNATING CERTAIN PARCEL OF LAND LOCATED AT BARANGAY ESTEFANIA, BACOLOD CITY, AS AN INFORMATION TECHNOLOGY PARK PURSUANT TO REPUBLIC ACT NO. 7916 AS AMENDED BY REPUBLIC ACT NO. 8748

Pursuant to the powers vested in me under Republic Act No. 7916, otherwise known as the Special Economic Zone Act of 1995 as amended by Republic Act No. 8748 and upon recommendation of the Board of Directors of the Philippine Economic Zone Authority, I, GLORIA MACAPAGAL-ARROYO , President of the Philippines, do hereby create and designate, subject to the provisions of Republic Act No. 7916 as amended, its Implementing Rules and Regulations, Resolution No. 00-411 dated 29 December 2000, as amended by Resolution No. 04-295 dated 20 September 2004 and Resolution No. 05-418 dated 28 November 2005 of the Board of Directors of the Philippine Economic Zone Authority, an area located at Barangay Estefania, Bacolod City, as Information Technology Park, consisting of Twenty Thousand (20,000) Square Meters, more or less, as defined by the following technical description:

Lot 1631-A TCT No. T-157078

A parcel of land (Lot 1631-A of the subdivision plan (LRC) Psd-32727, being a portion of Lot 1631 of the Cadastral Survey of Bacolod, LRC Cad. Rec. No. 55), situated in the City of Bacolod, Island of Negros. Bounded on the N., points 5 to 6 by Granada Bacolod Road; on the SE., points 6 to 1 by Lot 1631-B of the subdivision plan; on the SW., and NW., points 1 to 3 by Lot 1072; and on the W., points 4 to 5 by Lot 1630, both of Bacolod Cadastre.

Beginning at a point marked “1” on plan, being S. 75 deg. 09’E., 569.35 m. from B.B.M. No. 34, Bacolod Cadastre;

160.00 m. to point 2;

28.22 m. to point 3;

5.15 m. to point 4;

65.11 m. to point 5;

168.00 m. to point 6;

154.59 m. to point of

beginning; containing an area of Twenty Thousand (20,000) square meters , more or less. All points referred to are indicated on the plan and are marked on the ground as follows: points 1 to 6 by PS cyl. conc. mons. 15×60 cms. and the rest by PS cyl. conc. mons. 15×60 cm., bearings true; declination 1 deg. 20’E., date of original survey, March 1913 – March 1914, and that the subdivision survey, December 18, 1965.

IN WITNESS THEREOF , I have hereunto set my hand and caused the seal of the Republic of the Philippines to be affixed hereto.

Done in the City of Manila, this 18th day of January in the year of our Lord, Two Thousand and Seven.

(Sgd.) GLORIA MACAPAGAL-ARROYO

By the President: (Sgd.) EDUARDO R. ERMITA Executive Secretary

Source: Malacañang Records Office
